<sqoop xmlns="uri:oozie:sqoop-action:0.4">
  <configuration>
    <property xmlns="">
      <name>mapreduce.job.queuename</name>
      <value>fake_group</value>
      <source>because mapred.job.queue.name is deprecated</source>
    </property>
    <property xmlns="">
      <name>mapred.job.queue.name</name>
      <value>fake_group</value>
    </property>
    <property xmlns="">
      <name>fs.hdfs.impl.disable.cache</name>
      <value>true</value>
      <source>programatically</source>
    </property>
  </configuration>
  <arg>import</arg>
  <arg>-D oraoop.timestamp.string=false</arg>
  <arg>-D hadoop.security.credential.provider.path=jceks://hdfs/user/dev/fake.passwords.jceks</arg>
  <arg>--as-avrodatafile</arg>
  <arg>--verbose</arg>
  <arg>--connect</arg>
  <arg>jdbc:oracle:thin:@//fake.oracle:1521/fake_servicename</arg>
  <arg>--target-dir</arg>
  <arg>/user/data/ingest/mdm/member/fake_database/fake_mem_tablename</arg>
  <arg>--delete-target-dir</arg>
  <arg>--table</arg>
  <arg>fake_database.fake_mem_tablename</arg>
  <arg>--username</arg>
  <arg>fake_username</arg>
  <arg>--password-alias</arg>
  <arg>fake.password.alias</arg>
  <arg>-m</arg>
  <arg>10</arg>
  <arg>--fetch-size</arg>
  <arg>10000</arg>
  <arg>--direct</arg>
  <job-tracker>fake.trackeruri:8032</job-tracker>
  <name-node>hdfs://nameservice1</name-node>
</sqoop>
name: fake_mem_tablename_import
